div.p: A message broker that as many services as possible register to and notify the indexer.
Federation of message brokers should be possible. I.e. having one message broker per discipline.

How hard is it to implement RabbitMQ support into the dummy identifier service and the pit-service? As I currently do not move the data out of their old repositories, base-repo can not notify the Infexer for existing data (in other places).
